    "body": "## Purpose\n\nWe found that triton mla ending up being chosen on B200, even though cutlass mla was being \"forced\"\n\n```\nvllm serve deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder-V2-Lite-Instruct --load-format dummy\n...\n(APIServer pid=183965) INFO 08-12 10:27:33 [cuda.py:184] Forcing kv cache block size to 128 for CUTLASS_MLA backend.\n...\n(EngineCore_0 pid=184744) INFO 08-12 10:27:40 [cuda.py:240] Using Triton MLA backend on V1 engine.\n```\n\nThis is because `vllm/attention/selector.py:get_attn_backend` uses a cached read, so it doesn't notice the updated `envs.VLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND`\n\n## Test Plan\n\n## Test Result\n\n```\nlm_eval --model vllm --model_args pretrained=deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder-V2-Lite-Instruct --trust_remote_code --tasks gsm8k --num_fewshot 5 --batch_size auto\n(EngineCore_0 pid=287803) INFO 08-12 10:52:00 [cuda.py:237] Using Cutlass MLA backend on V1 engine.\nvllm (pretrained=deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder-V2-Lite-Instruct,trust_remote_code=True), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: 5, batch_size: auto\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.7551|±  |0.0118|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.7255|±  |0.0123|\n```\n\n\n",
    "created_at": "2025-08-12T14:50:02Z",
